# One Slack channel per line. Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
# Inline `# comments` after a value are also stripped.
#
# Either of these formats works — both resolve to the same channel ID:
#   C01234ABCDE
#   https://lambda.slack.com/archives/C01234ABCDE
#
# Channel IDs come from the Slack URL after "/archives/".

# Example entries — replace with your own channels:
# C01234ABCDE
# https://yourworkspace.slack.com/archives/C09MYP5K4H4
